{"tid":2262760,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳淑莊於酒吧開會 被票控違四人限聚令","createTime":"2020-10-29T10:41:23.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-29T14:47:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"84fb2658a4a54578bd4c6177e16bbe56464a4f3a","tid":2262760,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:41:23.000Z","msg":"前公民黨議員陳淑莊與香港中小企食店聯盟召集人林瑞華，於今年4月限聚令禁止多於4人聚集、酒吧須關閉14日期間，在酒吧「落半閘」開會，及後遭特首林鄭月娥及親建制陣營窮追猛打。陳淑莊、林瑞華及營運酒吧的負責人被票控違反限聚令等4罪，今在九龍城法院提堂。據控方指，是次事件只牽涉三名被告人。據庭外了解，控方案情指控陳淑莊及林瑞華與另外十多人聚集，但其餘與會人士未有被控。<br />\n<br />\n案件應辯方申請，押後至12月10日才處理答辯，以便辯方索取檢控文件及提供法律意見。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/ZOOJEM57BFCB3EA24KWVMEIJWQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FZOOJEM57BFCB3EA24KWVMEIJWQ%2F&d=2u41qa%2Bce9Gslgrzp%2F5KiiaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=ca888081\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201029%2FZOOJEM57BFCB3EA24KWVMEIJWQ%2F&h=d0548d64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201029/ZOOJEM57BFCB3EA24KWVMEIJWQ/</a>"},{"pid":"5d850e8e9d249f283184fe56c1c5f397233d3033","tid":2262760,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:42:10.000Z","msg":"我想落井下石"},{"pid":"e8686fd77b7d9157c29b6f9fa66125e951259354","tid":2262760,"uid":245849,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"黑警12人打邊爐加打女人冇問題"},{"pid":"4e375d0c0efaa22b5508507295afac12e3c9ef83","tid":2262760,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8686fd77b7d9157c29b6f9fa66125e951259354","tid":2262760,"uid":245849,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"黑警12人打邊爐加打女人冇問題"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-29T10:43:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im